# PakEscrow — Data Flow Documentation

> **Purpose:** This document explains where data enters the PakEscrow system, how it travels through each database table, which tables depend on which, and what outputs the system produces at every stage. It is written for developers, database engineers, product managers, and technical reviewers who need to understand the complete lifecycle of data — from a user's first registration to the final fund release and audit trail.

