## 10. Flow 8 — Withdrawal (Payment Out)

**Trigger:** A freelancer requests to withdraw earned funds to their bank or mobile wallet.

### Step-by-Step Data Movement

```
Step 1 — Freelancer submits withdrawal request
         POST /api/v1/wallet/withdraw
         Body: { amount, destination_type, destination_account }
         │
         ▼
Step 2 — Validation checks:
         READ [ wallets ] WHERE user_id = freelancer_id
         • available_balance = balance - locked_balance
         • Requested amount ≤ available_balance → allow
         • Requested amount > available_balance → reject with 400
         READ [ users ] to check kyc_tier and is_active = TRUE
         │
         ▼
Step 3 — BEGIN TRANSACTION
         │
         ├─ UPDATE [ wallets ]
         │    balance = balance - withdrawal_amount
         │    (optimistic lock via version column)
         │
         └─ INSERT [ payments ]
              direction    = WITHDRAWAL
              user_id      = freelancer UUID
              contract_id  = NULL (wallet-level withdrawal, not contract-specific)
              amount       = withdrawal_amount
              gateway      = JAZZCASH | EASYPAISA | BANK_TRANSFER
              gateway_ref  = pending (assigned after gateway confirms)
              status       = PENDING
         │
         COMMIT
         │
         ▼
Step 4 — Platform calls payment gateway payout API
         Gateway processes transfer to freelancer's bank/mobile account
         │
         ▼
Step 5 — Gateway sends confirmation webhook
         UPDATE [ payments ]
         │  • gateway_ref = gateway's payout reference
         │  • status      = SUCCESS | FAILED
         │
         ▼
Step 6 — If FAILED:
         BEGIN TRANSACTION
           UPDATE wallets balance = balance + withdrawal_amount  (rollback credit)
           UPDATE payments status = FAILED
         COMMIT
         │
         ▼
Step 7 — WRITE to [ audit_logs ]
         │  Action: WITHDRAWAL_REQUESTED → WITHDRAWAL_PROCESSED
         │
         ▼
Step 8 — WRITE to [ notifications ]
         │  Event: WITHDRAWAL_PROCESSED
         │  Channel: SMS + EMAIL
         │  Payload: "PKR X has been sent to your JazzCash account ending XXXX."
         │
         ▼
Step 9 — OUTPUT:
         • Freelancer's real-world account credited
         • wallets.balance reduced permanently
         • payments record with SUCCESS and gateway_ref
```

